deliverypoint

Descrição Recurso
Consulta todas os pontos de entrega GET /api/logistics/pvt/configuration/deliverypoint
Consulta ponto de entrega GET /api/logistics/pvt/configuration/deliverypoint/{deliverypointId}
Salva um ponto de entrega POST /api/logistics/pvt/configuration/deliverypoint
Exclui um ponto de entrega DELETE /api/logistics/pvt/configuration/deliverypoint/{deliveryPointId}/remove

Consulta ponto de entrega

longitude decimal Longitude
